{"word":"G5245 - ὑπερνικάω - hypernikáō - hoop-er-nik-ah'-o - More than conquer","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπερνικάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypernikáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-er-nik-ah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">More than conquer</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஜெயங்கொள்"},{"paragraph":"to be more than a conqueror, to gain a surpassing victory"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5228 - ὑπέρ - hypér - hoop-er'/5228\">G5228</a> and <a href=\"#/G3528 - νικάω - nikáō - nik-ah'-o/3528\">G3528</a>; to <i>vanquish beyond</i>, that is, <i>gain</i> a decisive <i>victory:</i> - more than conquer.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3527/3527\">G3527</a>, <a href=\"#/G3528/3528\">G3528</a>, <a href=\"#/G3529/3529\">G3529</a>, <a href=\"#/G3534/3534\">G3534</a>, <a href=\"#/G5245/5245\">G5245</a>"}]}